item.title: Robotics competition and solar eclipse and stuff
item.description: On Saturday, September 14, I went to the Space Coast Showdown, an off-season robotics competition with my team. I say “my” team, but I am new to the club. It was worth it to take the whole day off to be there and support everyone. I also learned a lot for how I can help contribute in the feature, as well as what competitions are truly like! {% include image.html url="/blog/media/spacecoast-place_small.
